        Create a structured network flick message for transmission through the cluster.
        Parameters:
        targetTableIdentity - Target table's identity in the cluster.
        galleryItem - Object representing the flicked item and its attached feedback.
        x - The X value of the flicked item's arrival location.
        y - The Y value of the flicked item's arrival location.
        targetAngle - Rotation of the flicked item on arrival.
        targetScale - Scale of the flicked item on arrival.
        xDir - The X value of the flicked item's direction on arrival.
        yDir - The Y value of the flicked item's direction on arrival.
        flickID - The unique ID of the flick message.
